Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:02.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Bye!\N-No breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:05.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks! I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:13.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!\NWatch where you're driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:17.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sorry.\N-Oh, really! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:20.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:24.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:27.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:35.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please accept our deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Master Ryutaro, she forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:48.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost positive\Nit's a St. Paulia School hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:49.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:55.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,MEIMI IS ENGAGED\NTO A MULTI-MILLIONAIRE'S SON!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:06.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Don't be depressed about being tardy.\N-Sister's lecture is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good, if that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:12.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It might be the Board Chairman\Nwho will give you a lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:15.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!\NI was only late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:19.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi! Please come\Nto the Chairman's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:21.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:28.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think something's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:32.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, it's you, Saruwatari.\N-The name's Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:39.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'd be called to\Nthe Chairman's office for being tardy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:43.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Who knows?\N-I think this is gonna be a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Meimi, come here.\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!\NI was tardy because a car--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:58.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's the one! No mistake!\NShe's the one I've been looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:00.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:05.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry about this morning.\NMy name is Ryutaro Tomikoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:10.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This morning you dropped your hat.\NThis gentleman came to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:15.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And also it's very sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:20.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...but Mr. Tomikoji requests that\Nhe be given the chance to date you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Date? With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:25.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This meeting is a God-given destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:29.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Love at first sight is\Nwhat you'd call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's all so sudden and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:38.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, if you accept, we shall\Nforget the tardy incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's a most courteous young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:46.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,To go out of his way for permission\Nto date one of our students.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:47.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:51.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Everyone tells me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:03:02.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I was sure you'd give that reply.\NWell, it's time we leave for our date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:06.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please take good care\Nof our Meimi. And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:12.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Regarding the contribution, I will\Nhave a company employee prepare it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:13.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Contribution? I've been sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:22.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Then we'll be back.\N- Have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:39.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A simple park like this\Ncan be quite refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of anywhere\Nfor a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I think your pureness is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:49.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's it!\NI should ask him for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:53.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then he'd be convinced\Nto forget this date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:56.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I've thought of something!\N-Wherever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:04:01.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to eat at Tetsujin-tei\Nand go to a musical at Bayside Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:05.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Let's not forget Wonderland Garden.\N-OK. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What a long line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, what's the matter?\NThe entrance is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But we've got to stand in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We came in without standing in line.\NAre you sure it's OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:37.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mother is sponsor of this restaurant\Nso we can come in anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I see. Ryutaro, your mother\Nis quite a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:45.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes. After Father's death, she's been\Nrunning the company by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:48.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But she does too much\Nwhen it comes to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:53.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Like deciding my fiancee.\NI'd like to decide on my own fiancee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:57.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-You're right.\N-Well, the musical is next, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:02.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Could you possibly be sponsors\Nof the Bayside Hall as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:10.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But Mother has special reserved seats\Nso there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:14.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This guy has no idea\Nwhat standing in line is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Shall we go?\N-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My parents will be worried\Nif I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:27.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Next time, we'll get permission\Nfrom your parents and enjoy our date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:32.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I can get home\Nby myself. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi! You're shy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:44.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is the fourth day. No matter\Nwhat Sister says, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, don't be such a spoilsport!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:51.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's right. You get to go\Nto all the popular places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:55.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's God's teachings. That's what you\Nget for accepting a date so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:06:00.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Seira. I'm leaving from\Nthe back gate so he won't catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:12.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Young lady, we've been waiting\Nfor you. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you're OK with it,\NI'd be glad to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:32.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Someone switched the heirloom necklace\Nmy mother left me with a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:39.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-This is it.\N-What? This shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mother is the sponsor\Nof this boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:49.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I'd like to select something for you.\N-You don't have to buy me clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:54.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're meeting my mother,\Nso please be conscious of your dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meet your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:59.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Tomorrow evening,\NMother's having a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I want to introduce you\Nas my fiancee there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:06.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Fiancee? You can't do that!\NI have no intentions to--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:09.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a junior high student!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:14.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You didn't hear the Chairman? I'm\Ndating you with intentions to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've heard nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:33.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-The news is all over the class!\N-Is it true he proposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:36.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He's the son of the owner\Nof the Tomikoji Group!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How do all of you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:42.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the source of the news\Nis from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:46.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., have you seen it?\NIt's my greatest scoop! Hey, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:49.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!\NAre you a show business reporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I said, be quiet, Saruwatari!\N-It's Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:57.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like Saruwatari,\Nhow about Sawagani?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:02.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's jealousy.\NHey, Meimi, Miss Popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:10.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, I'm sorry to disturb you\Nwhen you're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:14.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Seira, you too! Don't be mean.\NIt's work, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The job is for Miss Yumi Imamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:22.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She was a secretary for that\Nwoman entrepreneur, Madam Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:25.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But Madam Ranko has switched...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...her mother's heirloom necklace\Nwith a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:37.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,President, this isn't the necklace\Nthat I left with you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What in the world\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:43.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying\NI replaced it with a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:47.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know the real one.\NPlease give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stop this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:53.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you don't trust me,\Nthen you don't have to work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Leave here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:09:00.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yumi, who complained to Madam Ranko,\Nlost her job as secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:06.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NJust leave things to St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is the fake necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:13.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Madam Ranko always\Nhas the real one on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:17.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And your only chance is the party\Nthat's being held tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait, tomorrow's party?\NIs it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:25.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Right. Madam Ranko's real name\Nis Ranko Tomikoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Ryutaro's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:33.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The party tomorrow will include\Nforeign diplomats and other VIPs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:36.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...so the security will be\Nquite tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:38.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:43.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I think the best way to get in is\Nto go to that party with Ryutaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:47.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Seira! Do you know what\Ngoing to that party means?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I won't! I'll get in there\Non my very own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:10.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asuka Jr.! Kick the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:31.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tonight at the party hall, I'll be\Npicking up Madam Ranko 's necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:34.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A notice from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you going\Nto do about this ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I'm home!\N-Welcome home, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:47.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. I'll get tea for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:50.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but, Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:55.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!\NI've always wanted one like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:11:01.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,OK, you're getting sleepy.\NOne, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Papa, is this hypnotism?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:09.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But it's still in the research stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:14.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right, when I count to three,\Nyou'll become a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:17.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:29.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,When I count to three, you'll\Nreturn to normal. Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What? I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:36.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mother, you were a cat a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You used me as a guinea pig,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:44.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sorry. Here's the pendant.\N-You won't get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:47.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Forgive me!\N-No, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:50.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go? We're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:06.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come to the party\Nwithout telling your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ryutaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:12.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?\NBut that dress just won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Old man, bring it to me.\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:21.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He'll bring the dress I selected\Nfor you, so please change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:34.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Got no choice.\NI'll have to do as Seira said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Plus, that's a nice dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:48.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't need the security. As you\Nca n see, I have the necklace on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:52.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But St. Tail is able\Nto steal from anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:57.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,As I've said, that is why\Nwe've hired our own security guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:02.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Also, to have you roam around\Ndressed like that is a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:06.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you do your security\Nbut do it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:09.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please wait! I'm not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Meimi.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:48.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi. He really proposed to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That woman over there is my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's the necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Meimi.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's have one dance\Nbefore I introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:16.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- No, thanks. I can't dance.\N-I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:24.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Meimi, you're quite good.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:27.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where's Madam Ranko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:29.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:33.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ryutaro, I feel a bit ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:40.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry. I'll be fine\Nwith a bit of fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if she's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:59.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:06.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:14.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:31.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:36.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What's this?\N-Where's the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:38.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:44.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My necklace is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's appeared! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:52.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-It's St. Tail!\N-Hurry! Hurry! Get it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:59.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving with the necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:09.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:24.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:37.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one\Nwho's gonna catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:45.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy. Why is Ryutaro here?\NThat's it. It'd be just right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Miss St. Tail,\NI'd like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Take this fake back to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:12.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, you won't escape this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., please take care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:23.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What a dirty trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:26.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:34.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rats! What a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:51.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of this memory\Nof your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:03.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ryutaro! You got it back\Nfor me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know it's fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:09.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,As a reward, I'll do\Nanything you want me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:14.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then I don't want to marry\Nthe person you decided on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're not introducing me\Nto your mother now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:21.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I want to marry St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:28.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Her long, graceful movements.\NBeautiful hair. Her long, slim legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:31.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meeting her is a God-given destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Young lady, I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:40.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Master Ryutaro's got\Nthat illness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:45.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So, what's everybody\Ngonna say about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:52.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yumi was very happy that\Nthe necklace was returned to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:56.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Too bad about\NMr. Prince Charming, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:19:01.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cut it out! Love at first sight\Nis a big pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.\NWell, I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. seems to be in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to see him smiling again.
